archimate:DataObject.name: PartyProfileTypeCharacteristic
archimate:DataObject.documentation: A characteristic quality or distinctive feature of a PartyProfileType. The characteristic can be take on a discrete value; such as age; can take on a range of values; (for example; investment portfolio value of $50;000 - $100;000); or can be derived from a formula (for example; number of households = number of customer party roles).
